{"tid":681677,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣連續兩單分屍案","createTime":"2018-05-28T08:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T10:41:50.000Z","uid":153228,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b7081c9ca5604e7150f5dd8ea9f269e13ea55049","tid":681677,"uid":153228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:52:02.000Z","msg":"爭一半房產起殺機 桃園分屍案兇嫌把妻當「雞」殺<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/2439777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F2439777&d=bFYDW4yt9lkxTqnDWxBjIsP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=04da24fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F2439777&h=b2f1e766\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/2439777</a><br />\n<br />\n桃園市67歲老翁陳登科涉嫌殺害結縭40多年的68歲妻子簡美珠，並將屍體肢解成5大部分，刀刀都從關節處下手、手法相當俐落，據悉，陳翁過去曾在山區養雞、殺雞，他幾乎把妻子當雞來殺害，對於為何將內臟分離，他只是淡淡說解釋，避免搬動時會掉出來<br />\n<br />\n女兒在家中查找，竟在2樓房間立起的床墊後方發現裝2個裝有屍塊的袋子，她擔心爸爸返家滅證，提著其中一袋到附近派出所報案<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n帶住自己老母堆屍體去報案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台大畢業的27歲黃姓女子遭28歲朱姓健身拳擊教練男友殺害分屍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180528/1178658.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180528%2F1178658.htm&d=bFYDW4yt9lkxTqnDWxBjIsP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=26207cf3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180528/1178658.htm</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180528/1178630.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180528%2F1178630.htm&d=bFYDW4yt9lkxTqnDWxBjIsP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=63da07cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180528/1178630.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新北市板橋區一名20多歲的朱峻穎疑似和黃姓女友爭吵後，一氣之下在板橋國光路一處民宅殺害分屍。警方日前接獲女方家人報案，最後，在27日晚間發現7袋裝有屍塊的塑膠袋。而涉嫌殺人的朱男則是在今（28）日被人發現上吊在新莊衛福部台北醫院旁。<br />\n<br />\n另外，警方指出，抵現場後，在朱男包包內發現遺書，內容寫道遭女友欺騙才會憤而殺人，非常對不起爸媽。目前，警方已在現場拉起封鎖線，詳細案情還有待進一步釐清。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3314/3314005.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3314%2F3314005.jpg&h=d65b1c17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台大畢業的黃姓女子遭朱姓拳擊教練男友朱峻穎殺害分屍成7袋！黃女哥哥日前在臉書附上妹妹與女友的私訊截圖，<span style=\"color: red;\">只見黃女向友人訴苦，「他一直盧，煩」；而閨蜜則回應，「不要講太多廢話，不然到時候妳被分屍，這段話還要給檢察官，沒想到竟一語成讖。</span><br />\n<br />\n真係比佢個朋友烏鴉嘴UP中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45753e2b7834869917a14c0e477fda73c95a831d","tid":681677,"uid":153228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:52:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d82dcdaa5c0636fc15ed52f506dd4ec79147f33","tid":681677,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:08:59.000Z","msg":"應該帶黎香港殺再返台灣，咁咪無手尾囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1948da5ece33bb764ae1339e856148714b3ba470","tid":681677,"uid":20282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:41:50.000Z","msg":"呢啲要加幾多分？"}]}